name: Internet consumption Record Report
query:
select
    site as "TCIL Code",
    udise_code as "UDISE Code",
    siteschool_name as "School name",
    district as "District",
    block as "Block",
    date as "Date of Posting Bill",
    internet_service_provider as "Internet Service Provider:Select/Network Provider",
    data_usage as "Data Usage (Gb):Float/Data Usage (Gb)",
    monthly_bill_amount as "Monthly Bill amount",
    payment_date as "Date of Bill Payment",
    payment_details as "Transaction ID"
from `tabInternet consumption Record`;
